scene.message:
Nanjo: Ngh. The drowsiness{nl}
seems to press in with{nl}
a physical force.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hm, hmm?{nl}
I see! So this is the{nl}
boss room?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone, don't let your{nl}
guard down! ...or whatever.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey hey, there's a{nl}
super weird door in the{nl}
back~ Shall we go in?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A clearly suspicious{nl}
door. Best not approach it{nl}
carelessly.{waitkey}{clearbox}But standing here thinking{nl}
only wastes time...{nl}
Now, what to do?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It is a suspicious{nl}
door, but I sense no{nl}
evil presence from it.{waitkey}{clearbox}As Ayase says, going in{nl}
might be one option.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Alright! No use{nl}
dawdling around here.{nl}
Let's take a peek!!{waitkey}{ret}

???: Hahaha!{nl}
Spirited as ever,{nl}
aren't you, children.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I don't much like{nl}
peering into other people's{nl}
dreams. Feels like spying.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: When Ayase dreams,{nl}
does she come to this{nl}
dream world too, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Other people's dreams{nl}
are intriguing and fun,{nl}
y'know. Kekeke...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...The dream world.{nl}
Elly in{nl}
Dreamland.{waitkey}{clearbox}"Elly in Wonderland,"{nl}
so to speak.{nl}
Heehee...{waitkey}{ret}
